{"tid":1920574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東省通報一名深圳確診患者周二曾乘國泰航班抵港 再經深圳灣口岸入境深圳","createTime":"2020-03-11T14:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T17:44:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ce8cb637bfd882c2341f0c480604a6c8f7d530f4","tid":1920574,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"廣東省通報一名深圳確診患者周二曾乘國泰航班抵港<br />\n<br />\n廣東省衛健委表示，深圳市衛健委今天報告一宗境外輸入的新型冠狀病毒確診個案，患者2月7日前往法國出差，本月2日起出現發燒徵狀，<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期一從巴黎乘坐國泰CX260，星期二抵達香港後，經深圳灣口岸入境，當時體溫正常</span>，但由於有法國旅遊史並曾發燒，被送往蛇口人民醫院發熱門診，核酸檢測結果呈陽性。患者正在深圳市第三人民醫院隔離治療，情況穩定，廣東省衛健委已將相關情況通報本港衛生部門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273054&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1273054%26csid%3D261_341&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=ac7779b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273054&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"43a84ec1f57572d39d3f066e3ffd834b34a09b29","tid":1920574,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"呢幾日深圳有確診咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3002d80694159e6a09a616b56b927793c4d2b858","tid":1920574,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43a84ec1f57572d39d3f066e3ffd834b34a09b29","tid":1920574,"uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"呢幾日深圳有確診咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"有1單，唔通就係呢單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45970e5c9ce426b56187db8c2fd7c2ccb32d2222","tid":1920574,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy